cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

The paper deals with 3D object reconstruction using deep convolutional neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO). The use of probabilistic visual hulls and object mask and pose estimation also involves machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper may also fall under computer graphics (cs.GR) due to its focus on shape details and consistency.
